#. type: Content of: <sect1><title>
#: lfs-en/chapter09/consoled.xml:11
msgid "Configuring the Linux Console"
msgstr "Configurando o Console do Linux"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><indexterm><primary>
#: lfs-en/chapter09/consoled.xml:14
msgid "console"
msgstr "console"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><indexterm><secondary>
#: lfs-en/chapter09/consoled.xml:15
msgid "configuring"
msgstr "configurando"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter09/consoled.xml:18
msgid ""
"This section discusses how to configure the <command>systemd-vconsole-setup</"
"command> system service, which configures the virtual console font and "
"console keymap."
msgstr ""
"Esta seção discute como configurar o serviço de sistema <command>systemd-"
"vconsole-setup</command>, o qual configura a fonte do console virtual e mapa "
"de teclas do console."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter09/consoled.xml:22
msgid ""
"The <command>systemd-vconsole-setup</command> service reads the <filename>/"
"etc/vconsole.conf</filename> file for configuration information. Decide "
"which keymap and screen font will be used. Various language-specific HOWTOs "
"can also help with this, see <ulink url=\"https://tldp.org/HOWTO/HOWTO-INDEX/"
"other-lang.html\"/>.  Examine the output of <command>localectl list-keymaps</"
"command> for a list of valid console keymaps. Look in the <filename "
"class=\"directory\">/usr/share/consolefonts</filename> directory for valid "
"screen fonts."
msgstr ""
"O serviço <command>systemd-vconsole-setup</command> lê o arquivo <filename>/"
"etc/vconsole.conf</filename> para informação de configuração. Decida qual "
"mapa de teclas e fonte de tela será usada. Vários HOWTOs específicos de "
"idioma também podem ajudar com isso, veja-se <ulink url=\"https://tldp.org/"
"HOWTO/HOWTO-INDEX/other-lang.html\"/>. Examine a saída gerada de "
"<command>localectl list-keymaps</command> para uma lista dos mapas válidos "
"de teclas do console. Olhe no diretório <filename class=\"directory\">/usr/"
"share/consolefonts</filename> para fontes válidas de tela."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter09/consoled.xml:32
msgid ""
"The <filename>/etc/vconsole.conf</filename> file should contain lines of the "
"form: VARIABLE=\"value\". The following variables are recognized:"
msgstr ""
"O arquivo <filename>/etc/vconsole.conf</filename> deveria conter linhas da "
"forma: VARIÁVEL=\"valor\". As seguintes variáveis são reconhecidas:"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: lfs-en/chapter09/consoled.xml:38
msgid "KEYMAP"
msgstr "KEYMAP"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter09/consoled.xml:40
msgid ""
"This variable specifies the key mapping table for the keyboard. If unset, it "
"defaults to <literal>us</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Essa variável especifica a tabela de mapeamento de tecla para o teclado. Se "
"desconfigurada, [então] ela padroniza para <literal>us</literal>."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: lfs-en/chapter09/consoled.xml:46
msgid "KEYMAP_TOGGLE"
msgstr "KEYMAP_TOGGLE"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter09/consoled.xml:48
msgid ""
"This variable can be used to configure a second toggle keymap and is unset "
"by default."
msgstr ""
"Essa variável pode ser usada para configurar um segundo mapa de alternância "
"de teclas e é desconfigurada por padrão."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: lfs-en/chapter09/consoled.xml:54
msgid "FONT"
msgstr "FONT"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter09/consoled.xml:56
msgid "This variable specifies the font used by the virtual console."
msgstr "Essa variável especifica a fonte usada pelo console virtual."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: lfs-en/chapter09/consoled.xml:62
msgid "FONT_MAP"
msgstr "FONT_MAP"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter09/consoled.xml:64
msgid "This variable specifies the console map to be used."
msgstr "Essa variável especifica o mapa de console para ser usado."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: lfs-en/chapter09/consoled.xml:69
msgid "FONT_UNIMAP"
msgstr "FONT_UNIMAP"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter09/consoled.xml:71
msgid "This variable specifies the Unicode font map."
msgstr "Essa variável especifica o mapa de fonte Unicode."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter09/consoled.xml:77
msgid "An example for a German keyboard and console is given below:"
msgstr "Um exemplo para um teclado e console alemão é dado abaixo:"

#.  This is what is used by jhalfs for creating the vconsole.conf file.
#.      Whenever you want to change the following, please inform the jhalfs
#.      maintainer(s). 
#. type: Content of: <sect1><screen>
#: lfs-en/chapter09/consoled.xml:81
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<userinput>cat &gt; /etc/vconsole.conf &lt;&lt; \"EOF\"\n"
"<literal>KEYMAP=de-latin1\n"
"FONT=Lat2-Terminus16</literal>\n"
"EOF</userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>cat &gt; /etc/vconsole.conf &lt;&lt; \"EOF\"\n"
"<literal>KEYMAP=de-latin1\n"
"FONT=Lat2-Terminus16</literal>\n"
"EOF</userinput>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter09/consoled.xml:86
msgid ""
"You can change KEYMAP value at runtime by using the <command>localectl</"
"command> utility:"
msgstr ""
"Você consegue mudar o valor de KEYMAP em tempo de execução usando o "
"utilitário <command>localectl</command>:"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><screen>
#: lfs-en/chapter09/consoled.xml:89
#, no-wrap
msgid "<userinput>localectl set-keymap MAP</userinput>"
msgstr "<userinput>localectl set-keymap MAP</userinput>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><note><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter09/consoled.xml:91
msgid ""
"Please note that the <command>localectl</command> command doesn't work in "
"the chroot environment.  It can only be used after the LFS system is booted "
"with systemd."
msgstr ""
"Por favor, observe que o comando <command>localectl</command> não funciona "
"no ambiente chroot. Ele somente pode ser usado depois que o sistema LFS for "
"inicializado com o systemd."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter09/consoled.xml:95
msgid ""
"You can also use <command>localectl</command> utility with the corresponding "
"parameters to change X11 keyboard layout, model, variant and options:"
msgstr ""
"Você também consegue usar o utilitário <command>localectl</command> com os "
"parâmetros correspondentes para mudar o esquema, modelo, variante e opções "
"de teclado do X11:"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><screen>
#: lfs-en/chapter09/consoled.xml:99
#, no-wrap
msgid "<userinput>localectl set-x11-keymap LAYOUT [MODEL] [VARIANT] [OPTIONS]</userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>localectl set-x11-keymap ESQUEMA [MODELO] [VARIANTE] "
"[OPÇÕES]</userinput>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter09/consoled.xml:101
msgid ""
"To list possible values for <command>localectl set-x11-keymap</command> "
"parameters, run <command>localectl</command> with parameters listed below:"
msgstr ""
"Para listar valores possíveis para os parâmetros do <command>localectl "
"set-x11-keymap</command>, execute <command>localectl</command> com os "
"parâmetros listados abaixo:"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: lfs-en/chapter09/consoled.xml:108
msgid "list-x11-keymap-models"
msgstr "list-x11-keymap-models"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter09/consoled.xml:110
msgid "Shows known X11 keyboard mapping models."
msgstr "Mostra os modelos conhecidos de mapeamento de teclado do X11."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: lfs-en/chapter09/consoled.xml:115
msgid "list-x11-keymap-layouts"
msgstr "list-x11-keymap-layouts"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter09/consoled.xml:117
msgid "Shows known X11 keyboard mapping layouts."
msgstr "Mostra esquemas conhecidos de mapeamento de teclado do X11."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: lfs-en/chapter09/consoled.xml:122
msgid "list-x11-keymap-variants"
msgstr "list-x11-keymap-variants"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter09/consoled.xml:124
msgid "Shows known X11 keyboard mapping variants."
msgstr "Mostra variantes conhecidas de mapeamento de teclado do X11."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: lfs-en/chapter09/consoled.xml:129
msgid "list-x11-keymap-options"
msgstr "list-x11-keymap-options"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter09/consoled.xml:131
msgid "Shows known X11 keyboard mapping options."
msgstr "Mostra opções conhecidas de mapeamento de teclado do X11."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><note><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter09/consoled.xml:137
msgid ""
"Using any of the parameters listed above requires the XKeyboard-Config "
"package from BLFS."
msgstr ""
"Usar quaisquer dos parâmetros listados acima exige o pacote XKeyboard-Config "
"originário do BLFS."
